idth=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ikiyamay\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ikiyamay</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 22, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This is the best solution for sticky !!!! really!!!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works nice! 1A Support!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/niikk\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/ec5f2291caa3df866487b269d2373ba8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/ec5f2291caa3df866487b269d2373ba8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/niikk\" class=\"reviewer-name\">niikk</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 22, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Works very well and plugin support is awesome! :) Thanks!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fantastic Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" st