f=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dclaps\" class=\"reviewer-name\">DCLAPS</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">works great!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works as intended.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/azwick2\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6d9df0d87090cf64a6c7cdb38b04fc6e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6d9df0d87090cf64a6c7cdb38b04fc6e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/azwick2\" class=\"reviewer-name\">azwick2</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very simple, thank you!</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:114:\"Easily manage and create 301 &amp; 302 redirects. Simple to use &amp; validate redirects. Includes redirect stats.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:65:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/eps-301-redirects.2.52.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:2:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:70:\"https://ps.w.org/eps-301-redirects/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2047734\";s:7:\"caption\";s:24:\"301 Redirects admin area\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:70: